Program: Outlook
Title: Derren Brown: The magician’s secrets
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3csyhj9
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 27 Sep 2019
British illusionist and writer Derren Brown talks to Emily Webb about some of his famous stunts and how he used magic to overcome his social awkwardness. You can find more about his current show Secret below. Park Mak-rye has become one of South Korea’s best-known YouTube stars at the age of 70. Picture: Derren Brown on stage Credit: Matthew Murphy Show less